Disturbed Glucose Metabolism and Left Ventricular Geometry in the General 
Population.

Schmitt VH(1)(2), Billaudelle AM(3), Schulz A(3)(4), Keller K(1)(4)(5), Hahad 
O(1)(2), Tröbs SO(1)(2)(3), Koeck T(2)(3), Michal M(2)(6), Schuster AK(7), 
