Author information:
(1)Department of Cardiology, Cardiology I, University Medical Center, Johannes 
Gutenberg University Mainz, 55131 Mainz, Germany.
(2)German Center for Cardiovascular Research (DZHK), Partner Site Rhine-Main, 
